# Fonts

Font files for UI text and HUD.

## Recommended Fonts

For a shmup/sci-fi game, consider:
- Monospace fonts (good for scores)
- Futuristic/tech fonts for titles
- Clear, readable fonts for UI text

## Files

Place your .ttf or .otf font files here.

Examples:
- game_font.ttf - Main game font
- title_font.ttf - Title/logo font
- mono_font.ttf - Monospace for scores

**License reminder**: Only use fonts you have permission to use!

Ask @ui to load and use fonts in the interface!
